measurements.description: Twenty-five slightly cupped flowers and 17 buds on four up to 15.5-cm inflorescences; sepals ovate, white, overlaid light pink blotches and spots, light gold bars basally, light gold blush apically; petals elliptical, white, overlaid light pink blotches and spots, light gold bars basally, light gold blush apically; lip saccate, white, overlaid light gold, side lobes gold; column and anther cap white; substance firm; texture crystalline.
